All Known Implementing Classes:

public interface IDataStoreEditOperation<T>
IDataStoreEditoperation modifies data inside a given DataStore. Data requried for modification shall be passed in during initialisation. This operation is to be passed to IDataStoreEditable's mangadeData() method, where the perform() method of this class will be called.
